name: VoiceConversionPreset
description: The options for SDK preset voice conversion effects.

parameters.Off: Turn off voice conversion effects and use the original voice.

parameters.Neutral: A gender-neutral voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a female-sounding voice.

parameters.Sweet: A sweet voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a female-sounding voice.

parameters.Solid: A steady voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a male-sounding voice.

parameters.Bass: A deep voice. To avoid audio distortion, ensure that you use this enumerator to process a male-sounding voice.
